The paper discusses a method for link discovery in the Web of Data, which is a common topic in the database (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of clustering algorithms also suggests relevance to the information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
